data.meta_description: Mentko Grimmius was born on September 15, 1869 in Oostwold, Midwolda, Groningen, Netherlands, son of Berend Harms Grimmius and Elizabeth Woltjer. He was married on February 19, 1912 in Oostwold, Midwolda, Groningen, Netherlands to Jantje Kiewiet, they had 3 children. He was married on May 17, 1893 in Midwolda, Scheemda, Groningen, Netherlands to Jantje (Jennie) Ottens, they had 10 children. He died on June 23, 1939 in Grundy Center, Grundy County, Iowa. This information is part of Family tree familie Eilders by B. Eilders on Genealogy Online.
